keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.

unmap u
unmap x
unmap r
map u restoreTab
map qq removeTab
map <delete> removeTab
map 0 removeTab
map <c-q> removeTab
map <c-delete> closeOtherTabs

unmap [[
unmap ]]
map [ previousTab
map ] nextTab
map <c-L> nextTab
map <c-H> previousTab

unmap J
unmap K
unmap H
unmap L
map J scrollFullPageDown
map K scrollFullPageUp
map s scrollPageUp
map H scrollToLeft
map L scrollToRight

map ; goBack
map ' goForward
map x goBack
map c goForward

map { goPrevious
map } goNext

map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map a LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
